    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, sounds easy enough. a bit worried about the tea tree oil though, i heard it can be pretty strong. how much should i actually put on it so i don't burn the skin? also is it okay to use the ointment and the oil at the same time, or should i do one then the other? i just want to make sure i'm doing it right so i don't make it worse.",
